Jingying Xu and John Ryan presented at [2026 Linguistics Society of America (LSA) Annual Meeting](https://www.xcdsystem.com/lsa/program/a66baA9/index.cfm?pgid=462) held in New Orleans, January 8–10, 2026.

Jingying give two talks: *1*. **Learning telicity in context: Developmental evidence from Mandarin children.** *2*. **Beyond truth conditions: Context modulates telicity interpretation.**

John presented the talk **Reference, Aspect, and Event Completion in Mandarin Sentence Judgments**. 
